<title>字节花上百亿买的妇产医院，怎么样了？</title>
<link>http://weixin.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&amp;query=%E8%99%8E%E5%97%85%E7%BD%91+%E5%AD%97%E8%8A%82%E8%8A%B1%E4%B8%8A%E7%99%BE%E4%BA%BF%E4%B9%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%A6%87%E4%BA%A7%E5%8C%BB%E9%99%A2%EF%BC%8C%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E6%A0%B7%E4%BA%86%EF%BC%9F</link>
